PhonePe Data Engineering interview will be 17X easier with these questions
CTC = 30 LPA
EXP = 4+

If you're targeting a company like PhonePe,  These questions will help you:

🔹 Data Engineering 
1️⃣ How would you design a data pipeline to process millions of payment transactions per hour while ensuring reliability and data accuracy?
2️⃣ Suppose a transaction dataset arrives late or out of order. How would you design the pipeline to handle such scenarios?

🔹 SQL & Data Modeling
3️⃣ You have a table containing billions of payment transactions. How would you design partitioning and indexing to optimize analytical queries?
4️⃣ Write a query to find users who made transactions on three consecutive days.
5️⃣ How would you identify duplicate payment transactions in a dataset?

🔹 PySpark / Big Data
6️⃣ A Spark job processing transaction logs suddenly becomes 3× slower after new data is added. How would you investigate and fix it?
7️⃣ Explain how data skew happens in joins and what strategies you would use to handle it.
8️⃣ When would you choose broadcast joins vs shuffle joins in Spark?

🔹 Data Pipeline & Reliability
9️⃣ How would you implement data quality checks in a financial transactions pipeline?
🔟How would you design a pipeline to reprocess historical transactions if a bug is found in transformations?

